definition.text: This tutorial complements the information delivered in the Welcome to Superalgos Tutorial, focusing on the Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones and Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References, and more.

translations.text: Este tutorial complementa la información entregada en el Welcome to Superalgos Tutorial, centrándose en el Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones y Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References, y más.
Dieses Tutorial ergänzt die Informationen aus dem Welcome to Superalgos Tutorial und konzentriert sich auf Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones und Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References, und mehr.

Bu eğitim, Superalgos'a Hoş Geldiniz Eğitiminde verilen bilgileri tamamlar ve Düğümler Menüsü, Yedeklemeler, Klonlar ve Paylaşma, Eklentiler, Çalışma Alanları, Referanslar ve daha fazlasına odaklanır.
Этот учебник дополняет информацию, предоставленную в учебнике Welcome to Superalgos, уделяя особое внимание узлам Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones, Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References и др.
Tutorial ini melengkapi informasi yang disampaikan dalam Welcome to Superalgos Tutorial, dengan fokus pada Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones dan Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References, dan banyak lagi.
Deze zelfstudie is een aanvulling op de informatie in de Welcome to Superalgos Tutorial, met de nadruk op het Nodes Menu, Backups, Clones en Shares, Plugins, Workspaces, References en meer.
